{"tid":530284,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】買唔到生誕T灰左好耐，好唔開心 Day167 15/1","createTime":"2018-01-15T15:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T16:30:44.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e283955f071d41736ad321e3e23e43b9a2bd7d31","tid":530284,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係買唔到梅露生誕T灰左好耐，好唔開心嘅Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=IpVAHYfqpalG2qdNe%2B3tkwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ad74db18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=IpVAHYfqpalG2qdNe%2B3tkwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=16efb1ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我的直播頻道\t: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oracejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foracejan&d=IpVAHYfqpalG2qdNe%2B3tkwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=af7353c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oracejan</a><br />\n我的Facebook專頁:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=IpVAHYfqpalG2qdNe%2B3tkwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=16ef